<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>nfsy tʿẓm</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- nfsy tʿẓm qlby yrnm jsdy ysbḥ wyạ lsạny
 myn zyk myn fy jmạlk ạ̉sẖbʿ ʿmry wkly kyạny
 myn zyk yạ frḥẗ kl ạlạ̉yạm myn zyk ydy ḥyạty
 rạḥẗ wrḥmẗ wkẖyr wslạm
 2- nfsy ạrtạḥt jdạaⁿ lyk wlqt fyk mljạ̉ wḥmạyẗ
 wlqyt qrbk ʿz wnʿmẗ wạ̉mạnẗ mạlhạsẖ nhạyẗ
 myn zyk dh ḥbh lqlby zy ạlmyẗ llʿṭsẖạn
 myn zyk swạqyh mlyạnẗ trwyny bʿd ạlḥrmạn
 3- nfsy hdyt mr jfạhạ lmạ sẖmsk nwrthạ
 wsṭ ḥr ạlrḥlẗ ạ̹nt knt ḍlẗ ryḥthạ
 myn zyk qlby ydq yqwlhạ lsẖkẖṣk yhtf mjdạaⁿ mjdạaⁿ lyk
 kl zmạny hạʿysẖ ạsẖhd lk</lyrics>
